    "description": "《三国：归途》是一款融合了Roguelike玩法的卡牌构筑游戏，游戏将带领你重回三国时代，选择你的阵营，招募魏蜀吴三国的无双武将，构筑一套独一无二的牌组，过五关斩六将，不断攻城拔寨占据战略资源，最终称霸于三国乱世之上。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开启一场波澜壮阔的征程</h2><br>《三国：归途》以Roguelike卡牌构筑玩法为核心设计，你将能够选择魏蜀吴三大阵营，每一个阵营都拥有着各自独特的核心玩法策略。你将能够集结曾经活跃于三国时期的无双武将，运用各位武将的非凡武艺，助你过关斩将，攻城略地，达成一统天下的夙愿。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/df0d7f5c9b523e68b03fc4bd3271e6a8.poster.avif?t=1763376039\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/df0d7f5c9b523e68b03fc4bd3271e6a8.webm?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/df0d7f5c9b523e68b03fc4bd3271e6a8.mp4?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还原三国传奇兵种</h2><br>游戏还原了三国时期的传奇兵种，从虎豹骑、无当飞军、白马义从到藤甲兵，均可轻松收入麾下。步兵、骑兵以及弓兵三大兵种各自拥有着独特的战斗方式，而兵种之间更存在有相生相克的关系，更有着不同的阵法甚至法术来改变战局的天平。选择你心仪的部队，将其加入你的牌库构筑出最为强大的军团。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/9ca4e0e9e4817978197f8620e3dc9ad3.poster.avif?t=1763376039\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/9ca4e0e9e4817978197f8620e3dc9ad3.webm?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/9ca4e0e9e4817978197f8620e3dc9ad3.mp4?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >集结三国名将共同征战沙场</h2><br>在游戏中玩家将能够通过各种事件邀请三国历史中的知名武将加入你的队伍，并且在经历一次次的征战后，积累经验提升武将的天赋能力，让下一次的战斗变得更加轻松。当战斗变得艰难时，不妨尝试不同的武将组合，用丰富多变的策略来彻底改变战场的格局。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/a92502bfc08f723b850445d8c63495cd.poster.avif?t=1763376039\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/a92502bfc08f723b850445d8c63495cd.webm?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/a92502bfc08f723b850445d8c63495cd.mp4?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >历史成败由你书写</h2><br>滚滚长江东逝水，过去的历史早已注定。但在《三国：归途》中，魏蜀吴三国的故事才刚刚开始。游戏中有着上百种不同的卡牌和敌人，随机的事件和9种不同的关卡生成，每一次的征战都将有着不同的遭遇，而胜败与否则取决于你的选择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/34cc331d135f3332175d94ca55b131df.poster.avif?t=1763376039\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/34cc331d135f3332175d94ca55b131df.webm?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314770/extras/34cc331d135f3332175d94ca55b131df.mp4?t=1763376039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
